<div class="thumbcaption">
<div class="magnify"><a href="/wiki/File:Protectionfactorchernobyl30cm.png" class="internal" title="Enlarge"><img src="/skins-1.5/common/images/magnify-clip.png" width="15" height="11" alt="" /></a></div>
The protection factor provided by <b>30 cm of concrete shielding</b> where the source is the idealised Chernobyl fallout. <sup id="cite_ref-OECD_4-6" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-OECD-4" title=""><span>[</span>5<span>]</span></a></sup></div>
</div>
</div>
